snippet.title: Knights of Pen & Paper + 1 Deluxier Edition for Consoles
snippet.description:
An old school pen & paper RPG simulator comes to HD high-end game consoles: Nintendo Switch, Playstation 4 and Xbox One!

Nintendo Switch - 29th May 2018 - pre orders available!
PlayStation 4 - 29th May 2018 
Xbox One - 30th May  2018 - pre orders available!
